snippet: Fewer clinics, more Google searches for alternative methods.
abstract: Seth Stephens-Davidowitz Op-Ed article describes how Google search data reveals hidden demand for information about self-induced abortions in areas in United States where states have made it most difficult to get abortions; suggests this correlation is highly pertinent to Supreme Court case regarding Texas abortion law.
lead_paragraph: Fewer clinics, more Google searches for alternative methods.

headline.print_headline: The Return of the D.I.Y. Abortion
headline.main: The Return of the D.I.Y. Abortion
